The paper deals with the computation of document image quality metrics, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed solution involves the use of machine learning techniques to learn the behavior of the quality metric, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG), deep learning (cs.DL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
